frames.caption: A large, glowing green fish leaps dramatically from the water, its mouth open wide, as a person in a small wooden boat looks on in awe. In the background, several other boats with people are visible, set against a lush, forested riverbank. The scene is vibrant and fantastical, with the fish's luminescence contrasting against the natural surroundings.

frames.caption: A group of wooden boats glide along a serene river, surrounded by lush green forests. The water is disturbed by a vibrant splash, creating ripples and waves. The scene is set against a backdrop of dense foliage and distant hills.
frames.description: The image depicts a tranquil river scene with several wooden boats carrying people, moving through a forested area. The water is lively with splashes, suggesting movement and activity.
